BIC is a global leader in stationery, lighters and shavers, providing high-quality, affordable, essential products to consumers everywhere for over 75 years. As part of its ongoing commitment to sustainability, BIC introduced BIC ReVolution, the brand’s first full range of eco-friendly stationery items, thoughtfully designed to help consumers seamlessly incorporate more products that use recycled materials into their day-to-day routines. The BIC ReVolution line includes high-quality, long-lasting ball pens, mechanical pencils, permanent markers and correction tape that are each made of at least 50 percent recycled plastic, with BIC’s Ocean-Bound Retractable Ball Point Pen containing 73 percent recycled ocean-bound plastic. In addition, the paperboard used in the packaging for all products in the BIC ReVolution line is made of 100 percent recycled content and is entirely recyclable.
